##DESCRIPTION
##  Rational Functions: Finding Vertical and Horizontal Asymptotes
##ENDDESCRIPTION

##KEYWORDS('algebra', 'polynomial', 'asymptote')

## DBsubject('Algebra')
## DBchapter('Polynomial and Rational Functions')
